      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road immediately. If you're looking for a solid, well-loved vehicle that won't let you down, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
