    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit remains mechanically robust, with high-revving power delivery facilitated by individual throttle bodies and the Double VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered to the rear wheels through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement inspection and VANOS solenoid service. While the finish shows minor road-wear consistent with spirited use, the chassis dynamics remain exceptionally sharp due to refreshed bushings and a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution. A true analog masterpiece ready for its next steward.",
