    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 All-Wheel Drive Luxury SUV has been meticulously cared for and serves as a reliable, stylish companion for any commute. The exterior sports a deep metallic finish that still catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014purely cosmetic and typical for its mileage. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with premium leather seating that remains plush and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity sound system and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history that ensures the vehicle is mechanically sound. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brake feel is firm and responsive. This is a solid, honest vehicle that bridges the gap between everyday utility and high-end comfort.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
