    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really wonderful shape. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, well-cared-for vehicle that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
