    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally serviced. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the integrity of the rear suspension mounting points under load. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-enjoyed driver\u2019s car, the mechanical components remain tight, offering the sharp turn-in and linear power delivery this platform is renowned for. Recent work includes a valve adjustment and fresh rod bearings, making this a mechanically robust example ready for spirited use.",
